Description: NDOE, one of the most talented Bulgarian rappers, has been making hip-hop since 1994, when his first Amnesty band has released a cassette album. Then he's only 14, but the skills can not go unnoticed. In 2001, along with his buddy Dimitar (DRS), they released the cult disk "Урок # 1" that came out of Sniper Records. The album is unique because almost every artist is invited to another song.

Gery-Nikol Nikolaeva Georgieva better known simply as Gery-Nikol is a Bulgarian recording artist who rose to fame in late 2014 after participating in the third season of the singing competition X Factor Bulgaria.
Krisko is bulgarian hip-hop artist and producer.
